'''Fujairah Stadium''' is a multi-use [[stadium]] located in [[Fujairah]], [[United Arab Emirates]]. It is currently used mostly for [[association football|football]] matches and is the home ground of [[Fujairah SC]]. The stadium holds 10,645 people.<ref>[https://int.soccerway.com/teams/united-arab-emirates/ahli-al-fujirah/venue/ Information]</ref>

