'''San Pedro Pirates Football Club''' is a [[Belize]]an [[football (soccer)|football]] team.

The team is based in [[San Pedro Town|San Pedro]]. Their home stadium is [[Ambergris Stadium]].

The team competed in the [[2017–18 Premier League of Belize|2017–18]] edition of the [[Premier League of Belize]] for the first time.<ref>{{cite news|title=San Pedro Pirates to take part in 2017 Premier League of Belize|url=https://www.sanpedrosun.com/sports/2017/08/10/san-pedro-pirates-take-part-2017-premier-league-belize/|accessdate=11 August 2017|newspaper=San Pedro Sun|date=10 August 2017}}</ref>

