{{Infobox Stadium | stadium_name = Sirte Stadium | nickname = | image = | caption = | fullname = | location = [[Sirte]], [[Libya]] | built = | opened = | coordinates = {{coord|31|11|36.69|N|16|35|52.15|E|type:landmark_region:LY|display=title}}<ref name="goalzz_info">[http://www.goalzz.com/main.aspx?showstadiums=1&searchcountry=LY&stadium=4647 Sirte Stadium]</ref> | renovated = | owner = | operator = [[Khaleej Sirte]] | surface = | tenants = | seating_capacity = 2,000<ref name="goalzz_info"/> | dimensions = }}
'''Sirte Stadium''' is a [[multi-purpose stadium]] in [[Sirte]], [[Libya]]. It is currently used mostly for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches and is the home ground of [[Khaleej Sirte]]. The stadium holds 2,000 people.<ref>[http://www.goalzz.com/main.aspx?showstadiums=1&searchcountry=LY&stadium=4647 Sirte Stadium - goalzz.com]</ref>
